data.text:
2019/20: Season-highs: (p-a-r-3s-b): 11-4-6-3-2

High School: Played five years of baseball, four years of basketball, and three years of football…four-year starter in baseball, three year starter in basketball, and three year starter in football…First-team All-CNY… 11th-team All-State NY… B-Cany All-Star junior year…conference champions junior year…final 4 team…awarded MVP in basketball junior and senior year…MVP on offense in football senior year…batting tile senior year of baseball…basketball captain senior year and football captain sophomore and senior year…team earned second place in regular season and second in conference championship senior year…played on Syracuse Select and Powow…

PERSONAL: born Shawn D. Gashi September 29, 1998…Parents: Jennifer and Nikola…Siblings: Scotty, Skyler, Stephanie… Major: Sport and Leisure Management… Residence: West Monroe, NY…

Career-highs (thru 19/20): 28 min., 11 pts., 6 rebs., 4 assists, 2 blocks, 2 steals, three 3-pointers...

SHAWN... REVEALED

Among your friends, what are you best known for? Being a hot head

If animals could talk, which would be the rudest? Snakes

What is something that is really popular now, but in 5 years everyone will look back on and be embarrassed by? Fortnite

If you were in a life or death situation and told that if you didn’t impress them with your dance moves you would be killed, what dance moves would you bust out? The Jerk

If there was an Olympics for everyday activities, what activity would you have a good chance at winning a medal in? Netflix and chillin

What TV Series do you keep coming back to and re-watching? One Tree Hill

Best and worst flavors of ice cream. Best is birthday cake, worst is chocolate

What odd talent do you have? None really

If you unexpectedly won $10,000, what would you spend it on? Keeping it in the pockets

If you could have an animal as your sidekick, which animal would it be? Monkey

Name 5 things to take with you during a zombie apocalypse. Flare gun, machete, pistol, car, food/water

What is your favorite type of exercise? Basketball

A man walks up to you and says he is going to transform you into the animal of your choice and there’s nothing you can do about it. Which animal do you choose and why? An eagle, to be able to fly but not be eaten as often

You have seven dollars and five minutes at the grocery store. What do you buy? Gum, water bottle, sour patch kids and honey bbq flavor twists

If you had the World’s attention for 30 seconds, what would you say? Love everyone

If you had to work but didn’t need the money, what would you choose to do? Coach

If you could be a member of any TV-Sitcom Family, which would it be? Tanner family (Full House)

What simple task are you really bad at? Remembering

What product would you stockpile if you found out they were going out of stock and never be sold again? Good question
